summary:
Product Manager at the Platform team of Xentral ERP Software, an exciting scale-up focused on building a lean, modular ERP system. 

Previously Product manager at Dealroom.co, a global VC database.
MSc in Finance and Investments, Rotterdam School of Management. 
BSc in Economics and Business Economics at the Utrecht University, Honors Program.
